data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Welcome to your move-in ready haven nestled in a cul-de-sac. This home features a desirable floor plan with a spacious primary suite downstairs, including a large en suite bathroom and 3 walk-in closets, plus a private office with patio access. Enjoy formal dining and living areas, living room has barn doors for added privacy. The kitchen offers an inviting eat-in area with a gas range, while the family room impresses with tall ceilings and a cozy gas fireplace. Outside, a generous backyard includes a shed and playground, ideal for relaxation and outdoor activities. Explore your new home today! Conveniently located just minutes away from highways 67 and 20 for effortless commuting. Only a three-minute drive to the newly renovated Kidsville at Armstrong Park, offering enjoyable nearby recreation. Stainless steel refrigerator, washer, and dryer will remain.
